		Increase the standard size of the macro expansion buffer to 40k.

	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.60:
	* render/surface.h 1.17:
		Fix a couple of issues with eyeplits and occlusion culling.

	* librib2/parser.y 1.20:
		Remove light ID validation as it is perfectly normal to have duplicate light IDs
		in a multi frame RIB. The tracking of light IDs should be left up to the renderer.

