	* libshadervm/shaderstack.h 1.6:
		Fix bug, make sure that matrix variables are not identity marked when there components have been changed.
		Fix bug, was copying the wrong elements in the GetMatrix function.

	* render/texturemap.cpp 1.41:
		Fix handling of negative s/t values when mode is periodic.

	* libshaderexecenv/shadeops.cpp 1.11:
		Fix bug, make sure that matrix variables are not identity
		marked when there components have been changed.

	* librib2/parser.y 1.18:
		Fix bug in tag allocation in subdivision surface, wasn't
		allocating enough for the string and terminator.

	* render/attributes.cpp 1.18:
	* render/attributes.h 1.15:
		Implement a hash table for attribute lookup.

