2002-05-27  dsward2
	* libslxargs/slx.h 1.3:
		Corrected some symbol names that were incorrectly prefixed with
		SLO instead of SLX.

	* render/plugins.cpp 1.4:
		Added directives to conditionally omit the use of libdl when
		building libaqsis for Mac OS X by using the -DMACOSX_NO_LIBDL
		compiler flag.  I hope Apple will include the libdl.dylib in
		the next version of the OS and developers tools, and the
		conditional code can be removed.

