	* libshaderexecenv/texturemap.h 1.2:
	* render/texturemap.cpp 1.35:
	* render/texturemap.h 1.21:
		Move texture handling back into the core where it belongs, 
		other modules can access it via the new interfaces. This
		decision is due to the nature of the texture cacheing mechanism
		which is/will be very core specific.

