2002-03-31  pgregory
	* render/trimcurve.cpp 1.10:
		Fix bug in trim curve evaluation code. Was using an unsigned
		integer as an index, then checking for >=0 as a terminator.

	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.16:
		Small changes when tracking down quadrics bug, NYI.

2002-03-27  pgregory
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.15:
		Fix normal calculation to only do matrix multiply if the surface really can generate it's own normals.
		Take into account Orientation when calculating normals.

	* ribfiles/quads_test.rib 1.4:
	* ribfiles/std_st_test.rib 1.4:
	* ribfiles/uv_test.rib 1.4:
		Small changes to make tests more appropriate for regression
		testing, switch to using Sides 1 to test for Normal
		calculatioin problems.

2002-03-26  pgregory
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.14:
		Force circle function to use 4 arcs to avoid innacuracies in
		the bound calculation. Should look into further to find out if
		a more optimal solution exists.

