	* libcodegenvm/vmoutput.cpp 1.9:
	* render/shadeops.cpp 1.30:
		Fix long time annoying bug in shader VM. Multiple light sources
		would cause odd artifacts, due to illuminance construct in VM
		bailing out completely if one lightsource didn't contribute, 
		thus subsequent lightsources were missed.

