2002-02-15  pgregory
	* render/trimcurve.cpp 1.8:
		Fix bug where NURBS surfaces without trim curves were being completely trimmed!
		This was due to the fact that the trim check was based around the number of crossings
		being odd for interior surfaces, and 0 is even!!

	* librib2/librib.cpp 1.8:
	* render/micropolygon.cpp 1.24:
	* render/shadeops.cpp 1.26:
		Remove old texturedirectory code, superceded by trilinear mipmapping.
		Add support for attribute "trimcurve" "sense"

	* render/shadeops.cpp 1.27:
		Fix bug in illuminance/illuminate, incorrectly put fabs()
		around the cone angle acos check, hopefully have got it right
		this time!

	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.44:
		Fix bug in quantize, didn't quantize at all if ditheramplitude
		was zero.

