	* render/shadeops.cpp 1.9:
	* render/shaderstack.h 1.6:
	* render/shadervm.cpp 1.8:
		* Renamed SqImageValue to SqImageSample
		* Renamed CqImageElement to CqImagePixel
		* Restored depth and coverage data processing to CqImagePixel::Combine() (fixes the bug with rendering rgba images)
		* Eliminated warnings

	* aqsis/.cvsignore 1.3:
	* aqsis/aqsis.cpp 1.5:
		* Added "--help" and "--version" command-line options.
		* By default, a standard set of arguments is declared before processing any RIB files.  This behaviour can be turned off with the "--nostandard" option.
		* If no RIB files are specified on the command-line, automatically parses RIB from stdin.

	* shaders/Makefile.am 1.3:
		* Fixed bug in install target

	* libaqsistypes/color.h 1.2:
		 Added an output stream operator for CqColor, for debugging output

	* Makefile.am 1.10:
	* aqsis/Makefile.am 1.6:
	* aqsl/Makefile.am 1.5:
	* libaqsistypes/Makefile.am 1.4:
	* libcodegenvm/Makefile.am 1.4:
	* libddmsimple/Makefile.am 1.5:
	* librib2/Makefile.am 1.4:
	* librib2ri/Makefile.am 1.4:
	* librib2stream/Makefile.am 1.4:
	* libslparse/Makefile.am 1.4:
	* render/Makefile.am 1.9:
	* shaders/Makefile.am 1.2:
		* Updated install target

	* ribfiles/disp1.rib 1.2:
	* ribfiles/simple.rib 1.2:
	* ribfiles/skewtest.rib 1.2:
		* Updated sample RIB files to generate rgba images

	* librib2/librib.cpp 1.2:
	* librib2/librib.h 1.5:
	* librib2/parser.y 1.8:
		 Added "StandardConfiguration()" function to librib namespace, 
		which declares a standard set of Renderman arguments

	* configure.in 1.10:
		* Set the default install prefix to /usr/local/aqsis
		* Disabled shared libraries by default

	* INSTALL 1.2:
		* Updated installation directions

2001-06-11  pgregory
	* libddmsimple/ddmsimple.cpp 1.4:
		Rename SqImageValue to SqImageSample.

2001-06-10  pgregory
	* Makefile.am 1.9:
		Remove the old Readme.txt file.

2001-06-08  mbaas
	* render/attributes.cpp 1.5:
		Changed the default shading rate to 1.0.

2001-06-08  pgregory
	* Readme.txt 1.7:
		Removed, information now in README

2001-06-08  tburge
	* Renderer.dsw 1.15:
		Removed content from MS project to match recent changes.

	* shaders/shaders.dsp 1.2:
		Added files to MS project. to match recent changes.

	* render/cellnoise.cpp 1.4:
		Fixed cellnoise problem.  The first half of the permute table
		can not be simply duplicated to create the second half. 
		Duplicating it makes the cellnoise appear less random for multi
		value output such as returning color. Inshort gray occurs more
		than it should.  Need to update my webpage to fix permute's
		2048 and also the example table given.  Finally fixed it.

	* render/Makefile.am 1.8:
		Added teapot code to Linux build -- not really tested but
		atleast trying to avoid breaking it.  Sorry.

	* librib2/parser.y 1.7:
	* render/libaqsis.dsp 1.5:
	* render/ri.cpp 1.27:
	* render/teapot.cpp 1.1:
	* render/teapot.cpp 1.2:
	* render/teapot.h 1.1:
		Added teapot code, but still not finished.

	* ribfiles/skewtest.rib 1.1:
		Adding a skew transformation test never checked in from content
		test.

2001-06-07  mbaas
	* Doxyfile 1.2:
		Updated some settings so that doxygen doesn't abort with an error. Changes:
		- INPUT/RECURSIVE: Lets doxygen recursively collect all input files. The old INPUT line was obsolete anyway.
		- Disabled dot tool. Users who are familiar with doxygen/dot will know how to enable it again.
		- Disabled tree view (it takes VERY long to display the pages with this tree view)
		- Set TAB_SIZE to 2 to match tab size in Visual Studio (I hope this setting is stored in the *.dsw file in is not different everywhere)
		- Enabled INLINE_SOURCES (since this is Open Source you're probably interested to see the source anyway)

