2001-06-02  pgregory
	* Renderer.dsw 1.13:
		Add new projects libslparse and libcodegenvm

	* libslparse/funcdef.cpp 1.1:
	* libslparse/funcdef.h 1.1:
	* libslparse/ifuncdef.h 1.1:
	* libslparse/iparsenode.h 1.1:
	* libslparse/ivardef.h 1.1:
	* libslparse/libslparse.cpp 1.1:
	* libslparse/libslparse.dsp 1.1:
	* libslparse/libslparse.h 1.1:
	* libslparse/optimise.cpp 1.1:
	* libslparse/parsenode.cpp 1.1:
	* libslparse/parsenode.h 1.1:
	* libslparse/parser.y 1.1:
	* libslparse/scanner.l 1.1:
	* libslparse/typecheck.cpp 1.1:
	* libslparse/vardef.cpp 1.1:
	* libslparse/vardef.h 1.1:
		New library handles parsing of a .sl file into a parse tree, 
		which is then exposed to a backend code generator via a series
		of parse node interfaces defined in iparsenode.h, ivardef.h and
		ifuncdef.h.

	* render/shadervariable.cpp 1.5:
	* render/shadervariable.h 1.6:
		Remove superfluous shader type name array.

	* libcodegenvm/libcodegenvm.dsp 1.1:
	* libcodegenvm/vmoutput.cpp 1.1:
	* libcodegenvm/vmoutput.h 1.1:
		New library handles output of parse tree from libslparse into a
		format suitable for the Aqsis shader VM.

	* libcodegenvm/libcodegenvm.dsp 1.2:
	* libcodegenvm/vmoutput.cpp 1.2:
		Minor changes, now outputs version properly, and names the .slx
		file better.

	* libslparse/libslparse.cpp 1.2:
	* libslparse/parser.y 1.2:
		Fix problem with namespace intialisation.

2001-05-31  mbaas
	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.14:
	* render/micropolygon.cpp 1.7:
	* render/stats.cpp 1.3:
	* render/stats.h 1.6:
