	* render/renderer.cpp 1.21:
	* render/texturemap.cpp 1.8:
		Chnage to CqFile, the main CqFile now takes an optional
		searchpath string as a ';' separated list of pathspecs. 
		CqRiFile derives from CqFile and provides the ability to fetch
		the searchpath from the Ri options.

	* render/rifile.h 1.1:
		New CqFile derived class to handle Ri option searchpaths.

	* render/makefile.mingw 1.3:
		Removed MinGW support.

