2001-05-08  pgregory
	* render/Render.dsp 1.6:
	* render/imagebuffer.cpp 1.6:
	* render/imagebuffer.h 1.5:
	* render/micropolygon.cpp 1.5:
	* render/micropolygon.h 1.4:
	* render/nurbs.cpp 1.3:
	* render/patch.cpp 1.6:
	* render/polygon.cpp 1.5:
	* render/quadrics.cpp 1.4:
	* render/render.cpp 1.6:
	* render/renderer.cpp 1.11:
	* render/renderer.h 1.9:
	* render/ri.cpp 1.10:
	* render/scene.cpp 1.2:
	* render/scene.h 1.3:
	* render/subdivision.cpp 1.6:
	* shadowmap/shadowmap.dsp 1.4:
		Removed scene storage, now GPrims are piped directly to the image buffer, and can be culled immediately if necessary.
		Moved the shading of grids into the image buffer and out of the dice routines.
		Got rid of the need to bound grids, they are placed in the same bucket as the GPrim they come from.

	* render/vector2d.cpp 1.2:
	* render/vector2d.h 1.3:
	* render/vector3d.cpp 1.2:
	* render/vector3d.h 1.3:
	* render/vector4d.cpp 1.2:
